data.description: This charming home boasts generously sized bedrooms, with vaulted ceiling in living room giving the home an open, spacious feeling. Step outside onto the large back deck, perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying the outdoors. Situated on a nicely sized .19 acre lot. Its convenient location ensures easy access to a variety of local amenities, adding to the appeal of this wonderful home. This residence presents a unique opportunity to enjoy comfortable living in a sought-after location. Don't miss the chance to make this property your own.
